<p>
  A solution for some of the top ‘big iron’ brands gave a refreshed look of what
  it looked like to get mail. The top brands include Scag mowers, Ferris mowers,
  and Wright mowers.
</p>

<p>
  Ferris mowers are known for their suspension. You can rely on a mower that
  gives you support and comfort with the smoothest ride- all with the enhanced
  large forefront suspension springs. This direct mail piece featured the
  suspension springs in the design, and read “Experience Suspension” along the
  bottom of the tube.
</p>

