<p>
  Wright mowers are the original stand-on mower. With the standard of
  innovation, Wright mowers are safer and more efficient than riding mowers,
  allowing users to jump on and off. These mowers also take up less space on
  work trucks, and can fit in tighter, harder to cut sloped areas zero turns are
  not built for.
</p>

